Well, here's the question we want to ask this morning.

00:00:04.809 --> 00:00:09.410
Is it actually possible to speed up the day of Jehovah?

00:00:09.410 --> 00:00:17.289
Well, if we look at our text this morning in 2 Peter chapter 3, and verse 11, we've had

00:00:17.289 --> 00:00:23.829
that red for us, so we know that expression at the end that we should consider what sort

00:00:23.829 --> 00:00:29.890
of people you ought to be in holy acts of conduct and deeds of godly devotion.

00:00:29.890 --> 00:00:36.890
