00:00:36.890 --> 00:00:39.049
of Jehovah.

00:00:39.049 --> 00:00:44.689
Well now if you look at the footnote on this expression in verse 12, you'll notice that

00:00:44.689 --> 00:00:52.890
the expression keep close in mind literally means to speed up the day of Jehovah.

00:00:52.890 --> 00:00:54.570
Well now how can we do that?

00:00:55.049 --> 00:01:01.369
Well, it's true, we cannot bring the day forward of Jehovah even one day, nor can we

00:01:01.369 --> 00:01:03.969
move it back even one day.

00:01:03.969 --> 00:01:05.769
