00:01:07.689 --> 00:01:14.890
But how can we then speed up the day of Jehovah as it says there in verse 12?

00:01:14.890 --> 00:01:18.689
Well we keep that day close in our mind.

00:01:18.689 --> 00:01:21.450
We never let it be out of our sight.

00:01:21.489 --> 00:01:26.569
As the footnote also says, we eagerly desire it.

00:01:26.569 --> 00:01:33.489
Well now if we're persons like that, Peter says that we're going to be busy in deeds of

00:01:33.489 --> 00:01:35.370
godly devotion.

